Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.91,0:00:02.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all started with the Sacred Tree.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:04.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fighting and searching\nfor our dreams...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:06.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and a strong bond\nis formed between us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:07.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A new hope!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:09.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A bright future begins now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:12.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Demon rats go on a wild stampede.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what is Naraku's aim\nin causing this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:17.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Kohaku, the one who\nmanipulates these rats,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:19.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}comes to a decision after\nmuch anguish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:21.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final shard guides us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:22.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the other side of the well,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:24.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}a new day awaits in\nthe age of warring states!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:25.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Feudal Fairytale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.37,0:00:26.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:11.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not healed yet,\NHakudoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:16.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's because of that arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:21.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:40.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:46.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That same arrow broke my barrier\nonce before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:48.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:53.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only she could imbue an arrow\nwith so much will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:55.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't you go immediately\nto kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:58.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I cannot sense her presence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:01.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is she seriously trying to\nhide herself?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:06.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then it will mean that she\nhas not completely recovered.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:11.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must lure her out now\nand finish her off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:20.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no mistake...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku and Hakudoshi's heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:25.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}is Hakudoshi's other half-\nthat infant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Neither Naraku nor Hakudoshi\nhave died.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:30.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it because they are demons?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What must I do to defeat Naraku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:34.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey {\i1}Kohaku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:35.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:39.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You haven't been told?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:41.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That infant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:48.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After you took it out of that castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:50.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,where were you supposed\nto take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:52.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That infant?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if it meant killing everyone\nin the castle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:58.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was ordered to take it\nout of the castle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:05.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What would you do\nif you knew its whereabouts?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm always telling {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:10.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,one day, that Sacred Jewel shard\nwill be removed from your body
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:11.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:14.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If Naraku isn't killed,\nyou won't be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:17.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the infant is found,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:19.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}can Naraku be killed?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagura is trying to\nbetray Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:25.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:33.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't have them finding out...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I've remembered everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:42.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I'm after Naraku's life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:45.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I keep pretending to\nbe his slave,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:48.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll come across that infant again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:53.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until that time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:56.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must not disobey Naraku's orders.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come one, come all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:09.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With this amazing sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:11.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall cut this sheet of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From one into two!\NThen two into four!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:14.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then four in eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:18.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then 16, 32 and 64 pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:25.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, where did Inuyasha\ngo leaving us here like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:26.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm....{\i0} I {\i1}wonder....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:28.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:30.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:34.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To the spot where he\nlast met Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:36.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But {\i1}that's....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:37.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:39.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay. He can do as he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:05:59.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:02.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:07.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've hidden yourself away again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:12.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You haven't recovered all\nyour strength yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:19.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey {\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:24.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we have gone\nwith him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:28.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He probably wanted to\ntalk to Kikyo alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:31.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you have such\nan understanding heart, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:32.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:36.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Inuyasha is such a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:40.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Still wagging his tail and\ngoing after a woman from his past!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:42.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Although it is said about dogs:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:43.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once a pet,\na dog never forgets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:46.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who's a pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And so?\NWhat did you talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:52.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:55.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't have to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:56.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:07:00.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why would I have to lie?\NStupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:01.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:06.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:07.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:12.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was kind to you and\nlet you go off by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At least be up front about\nwhat you talked about!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:17.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:22.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no sense in\nhaving any consideration for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:23.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:29.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess Kagome was feeling\nhurt, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Poor Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:34.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It doesn't pay to be\nunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:36.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You {\i1}guys....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:45.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here, I got it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:56.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hakudoshi, lure Kikyo out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And {\i1}take....{\i0} Let's {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:00.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Kohaku.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do as Hakudoshi tells you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:03.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The method is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:08.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just make sure that Kikyo\ncannot stay in hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:10.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You let your subordinates\neat the meat of their prey,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:27.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and devour the bones yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are Zushinezumi....huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:32.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:38.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brat....{\i0} Are you a survivor\nof this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:39.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:42.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I had a hankering for\nbones like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:50.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're quite skilled, Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:59.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bring that little shrine that\nhe has on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:00.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:04.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't make a mistake\nand open it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:06.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:38.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}T- That's...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:57.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you sense something strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:12.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:15.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:20.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:23.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:28.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are they being pursued\nby something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:29.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:31.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:38.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!\NStop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:40.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:44.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:44.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They've increased!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:47.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew {\i1}it....{\i0} Zushinezumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:47.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:50.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why these...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:51.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:53.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These {\i1}Zushinezumi....{\i0}\NThe more you kill, the more they increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:55.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How do you exterminate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:56.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With toxic smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But without special medicinal {\i1}herbs....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:00.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't have them with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:01.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unfortunately....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then there's only {\i1}this....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The village was attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:17.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Luckily, my grandson and I were up\nin the mountain behind the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:18.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,everyone else in the {\i1}village....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:27.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:30.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You called them Zushi....nezumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:32.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There should be a large rat\nwho is their chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:36.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He keeps the rats in a\nminiature shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,which he carries on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:41.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And he releases them to\nkill humans and animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:44.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He only attacks what\nhe plans to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:47.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've never heard of a large\npack of rats attacking a village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:50.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's bound to be many more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can smell rats far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And it's as though their numbers\nare steadily increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:57.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-Increasing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:02.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You two must get further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:04.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're gonna check to see\nwhat's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:16.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can smell them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The way they're increasing\nisn't normal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:21.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on anyway?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:32.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They keep coming, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:39.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The rats will scatter everywhere\nand attack wherever humans live.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:48.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,R-Rats?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:50.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And wherever they go,\ntheir numbers will increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:09.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In time, this land will\nbe devoured by rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will Kikyo come out of hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:13.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I suppose she will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:20.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She'll soon know what's\nhappening here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Resorting to this,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:25.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}just to lure Kikyo out of hiding!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:38.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kocho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:39.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:41.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is something I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is in the western mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:00.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everywhere is overrun by rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:03.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:05.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You said that Zushinezumi increase
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:07.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in proportion to the numbers\nwhich are cut, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:07.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:09.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They don't die even if\nyou cut them,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:10.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so they keep increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:14.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since they've spread so far,\nwe can't trace the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:17.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By source, you mean\nthe miniature shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:18.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard that if you destroy\nthe shrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the rats will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:29.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku and Sango are\nso late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:35.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez! Why do I have to wait\ninside the barrier, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:36.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When you get mad,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you tend to go crazy and swing\nyour sword around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:40.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That'll only make the rats\nincrease.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:43.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you implying that\NI'm stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:46.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow, for someone who's stupid,\nyou figured that out quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Owwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:48.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Saimyosho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does that mean Naraku is\nbehind
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:57.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,this rampage of the Zushinezumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:00.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:04.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't think he died\nin that fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:10.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, they've returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:14.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you saw them, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:16.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Saimyosho?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:17.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:22.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is Naraku looking for us\nto get revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:23.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}think....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:26.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He wants us to know that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:28.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he's the one behind\nall this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:30.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaddya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:32.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Doesn't it seem as though
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:34.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he's trying to lure\nsomeone out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:37.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Us....or....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:39.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:41.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:45.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku's after Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:52.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mistress {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:55.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kocho is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:00.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mistress {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:04.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here is the branch of\n{\i1}ogatama{\i0} which you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:08.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:10.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Asuka, Kocho,\nwe are descending the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:08.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What {\i1}is....?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:12.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The rats who were scattered\nare starting to gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:16.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's like they're headed\nfor one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:17.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:19.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're forming one line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:25.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Somewhere, there is a {\i1}mayose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:26.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mayose?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:30.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A spell that lures demons together,\nthen destroys them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:33.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But only one with immense\nspiritual power can cast such a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:36.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only one capable of this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}is Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:41.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the end of this flow of rats\nis Kikyo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:43.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:45.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:48.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll try to go to the source,\nwhere the rats are coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:49.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:50.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It bothers {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:54.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that the number of rats\nhasn't decreased at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:57.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Which means that the shrine\nis still releasing rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:00.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So we must go to the source\nor this will not end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's split into two groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:04.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go with Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:09.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:11.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo has made her move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku, you stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:18.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Guard the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:21.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not close the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:24.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:30.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say {\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:34.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If Kikyo is up ahead,\ndo you think Naraku will appear, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:34.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:36.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:39.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku is after Kikyo's life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you scared of Naraku, Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:46.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then you shoulda gone with\NMiroku and Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:47.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When you and Kikyo meet
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:51.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and that funny feeling\ncomes over you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:53.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who's gonna console Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:55.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:57.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you get it, you two-timing dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:00.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keep it up and\NI'll drop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:03.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm scared, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:11.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Namuhachiban daibosatsu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:22.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo! Do you have anything\nthat rats hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:24.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fire bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:38.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Make your escape now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:39.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:44.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:49.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How's that?!\NThe power of my fire bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:54.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:19:59.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The rats are climbing something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:04.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-It looks like a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:09.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It reaches up all the way\nto heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:13.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The rats are disappearing\ninto the {\i1}sky....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:16.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this the {\i1}mayose?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:26.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This village seems to have\nbeen devoured some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:30.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, it was in the path\nof the rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:32.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How {\i1}cruel....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry, Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:40.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:42.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo has come out of hiding.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do not close the doors.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:49.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That bastard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:50.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was enjoying this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:55.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I close these doors,\nthe rats will stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may save some lives.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:05.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm being watched...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I close the doors,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:12.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku will know that my\nmemory has returned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:16.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:17.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:23.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Were you behind this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:26.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:29.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:32.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On my way here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:35.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I saw countless villages\ndevoured by rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:41.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How I wish you were not\na part of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:50.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I cannot....disobey my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:55.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:21:57.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.37,0:23:48.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you know how many villages were\ndevoured
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.17,0:23:50.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,just to lure Kikyo out of hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.14,0:23:52.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When you see him, tell {\i1}him....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.21,0:23:55.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as you keep running away\nfrom Naraku,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.41,0:23:57.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,this will happen over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.58,0:24:00.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku, you're going to end up\nfodder for the rats, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.95,0:24:04.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sister.\NBut I cannot disobey my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.62,0:24:09.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Kohaku's Decision and Sango's Heart"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.62,0:24:12.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must defeat Naraku as soon as possible!
